metadata.name: House 1 #162
metadata.description:
Ethopia is a medieval fantasy MMORPG game that takes you back in time to discover sites of outstanding beauty and rich history, captivating and cradled by many legends. The houses can be found in different cities of the ethopia worldmap. Only a set number of houses will be produced for each city, there will never be any more houses produced. 

These homes offer endless privileges, only house owners can stake EPIA token and this NFT provide staking power multipliers, storage for your game items, MP refillers, the ability to host parties, organize mini-quests, airdrops, discord roles and more to come.

Homeowners get additional benefits within the world of Ethopia.
Learn more at https://ethopia.online
